<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c01"/><p id="pI01p0107c0101">夫真源寂寥。妙相絕尋。凝靖也則<note n="0107001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">毦＝邪【史】</note><app n="0107001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">毦</rdg></app>風<note n="0107002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04152;＝鼓【史】</note><app n="0107002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04152;</rdg></app>世。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c02"/>絕尋也則群師見軌。致令蒼生繼泥犁之因。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c03"/>是　以　大慈。府愍含識。誕&CB00528;迦維。使天人
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c04"/>咸　　信。□那比轍郁穆之風於斯流矣。清
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c05"/>信士□弟□□建義大都督巢山監軍鎮遠
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c06"/>將軍前平陽令高涼令青州安平縣開國侯
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c07"/><note n="0107003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30694;＝巨【史】</note><app n="0107003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">巨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30694;</rdg></app>始光。自惟□因浮<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淺</unclear>。樹業彫微。生於季葉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c08"/>長逢兵亂。王道時屯。群飛未<note n="0107004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00188;＝接【史】</note><app n="0107004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">接</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00188;</rdg></app>。妖熒充斥。忠
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c09"/>良異路。值龍變虎爭之秋。列士立功之會。常
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c10"/>思納肝之誠。又慕孫賓之節。契<note n="0107005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30684;＝闊【史】</note><app n="0107005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">闊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30684;</rdg></app>戎行。<note n="0107006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30689;＝夷【史】</note><app n="0107006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30689;</rdg></app>嶮
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c11"/>備經。艱危之中。痤o私願。遂心存至道。追慕
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c12"/>玄津。福祐無違。精誠剋立。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">蒞</unclear>宰向周。<note n="0107007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04130;＝缺【史】</note><app n="0107007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">缺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04130;</rdg></app><note n="0107008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13901;＝期【史】</note><app n="0107008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">期</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13901;</rdg></app>月
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c13"/>之化。綏民撫政。乏童雉之惠。慶福嘉祉。寔由
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c14"/><note n="0107009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30695;＝靈【史】</note><app n="0107009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">靈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30695;</rdg></app>蔭。託根挺拔。因助獲善。仰惟三寶恩重。思
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c15"/>著<note n="0107010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30685;＝聚【史】</note><app n="0107010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30685;</rdg></app>沙之功。尋優瑱養正而遺風。想育王<note n="0107011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB14695;＝叔【史】</note><app n="0107011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">叔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB14695;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c16"/>世而繼範。故葉公好龍。感至義而見真。目連
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c17"/>慕德。刻圖像而尊奉。乃藉本宿心。兼<note n="0107012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02420;＝規【史】</note><app n="0107012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02420;</rdg></app>古則。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c18"/>輒<note n="0107013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30568;＝率【史】</note><app n="0107013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">率</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30568;</rdg></app>文武。鄉豪長秀。並<note n="0107014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30686;＝竭【史】</note><app n="0107014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">竭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30686;</rdg></app>丹誠。敬造石像一
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c19"/>區。然<note n="0107015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30687;＝蘊【史】</note><app n="0107015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蘊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30687;</rdg></app>石懸峰。漏影侍時。含相好以&CI0003;。賴
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c20"/>良匠而顯<note n="0107016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30696;＝姿【史】</note><app n="0107016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">姿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30696;</rdg></app>。妙狀熙怡。若琲e之滲金容。彫
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c21"/>文瑩飾。則昱離朱之目矣。且功起朱明。流火
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c22"/>已就。<note n="0107017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30688;＝雖【史】</note><app n="0107017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30688;</rdg></app>申子之營祇<note n="0107018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00035;＝園【史】</note><app n="0107018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00035;</rdg></app>未能加也。令<note n="0107019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31176;＝尟【史】</note><app n="0107019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31176;</rdg></app>信之
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c23"/>徒。睹<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">&CB00528;</unclear>追菩提之原。脩道之士。損生必證于
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c24"/>寂滅。增道改迷。豈非善歟。其詞曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c25"/>大猷淵凝。體絕有<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>。慧照万境。妙相沖虛。<app source="0107006" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30689;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c26"/>尒生滅。殄茲四衢。湛然常樂。非<note n="0107020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30690;＝毀【史】</note><app n="0107020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">毀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30690;</rdg></app>非譽。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c27"/>玉<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">響</unclear>掇聞。玄光潛暉。群<note n="0107021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30691;＝邪【史】</note><app n="0107021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30691;</rdg></app>樹黨。迷根<note n="0107022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30692;＝喪【史】</note><app n="0107022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30692;</rdg></app>譏。九
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c28"/>惚<note n="0107023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04991;＝裁【史】</note><app n="0107023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">裁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04991;</rdg></app>繁。糸髮靡依。謬匠濫敷。苦海長歸。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c29"/>大覺含悲。府悼沉淪。晦接群醜。鹿野垂仁。導
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c30"/>迷布正。淳風日新。望波向化。悟體歸真。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c31"/>惟仁英哲。道性純醲。秀石名山。摸此聖容。每
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c32"/>詠優瑱。繼茲遺蹤。非但普益。慶願必從。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c33"/>儒才雅士。並慕玄津。丹誠<note n="0107024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30693;＝款【史】</note><app n="0107024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">款</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30693;</rdg></app>篤。唯君與臣。心
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c34"/>專福善。造<note n="0107025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04130;＝垂【史】</note><app n="0107025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">垂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04130;</rdg></app>十旬。神相炳著。積薀方申。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c35"/>維大魏大統六年歲次庚申七月丙子朔十
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c36"/>五日庚寅。<app source="0107003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">巨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30694;</rdg></app>始光合縣文武邑義等。仰為
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c37"/>皇帝陛下。大丞相。七世所生父母。存亡眷屬。
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c38"/>為一切眾生敬造。齋主力法
<lb ed="C I" n="0107c39"/>邑師高涼三藏比丘辯賢。副齋主王遵平。</p>
</div2>
